♪ <i>This is my heaven, baby</i> ♪

1937
01:51:51,465 --> 01:51:57,171
♪ <i>Day and night in my zone</i> ♪

1938
01:51:57,304 --> 01:51:59,306
♪ <i>The feeling</i>
<i>Flows through me</i> ♪

1939
01:51:59,440 --> 01:52:01,008
♪ <i>Heaven's where we meet</i> ♪

1940
01:52:01,141 --> 01:52:04,678
♪ <i>Happy we lovin'</i>
<i>We lovin' our lives</i> ♪

1941
01:52:04,813 --> 01:52:08,315
♪ <i>Things I wished to see</i>
<i>Seem to come to be</i> ♪

1942
01:52:08,449 --> 01:52:11,151
♪ <i>I seek the truth, I'm honest</i>
<i>Hey</i> ♪

1943
01:52:11,285 --> 01:52:14,388
♪ <i>The moon is singin' our song</i> ♪

1944
01:52:14,522 --> 01:52:16,323
♪ <i>Say we find</i>
<i>What we're searchin' for</i> ♪

1945
01:52:16,457 --> 01:52:18,359
♪ <i>The love that we holdin'</i> ♪

1946
01:52:19,126 --> 01:52:21,495
♪ <i>Another adventure unfolds</i> ♪

1947
01:52:21,629 --> 01:52:23,832
♪ <i>I been dreamin' about it</i>
<i>Yeah</i> ♪

1948
01:52:23,965 --> 01:52:26,133
♪ <i>Dreamin' about it</i> ♪

1949
