♪ <i>I think I'm home</i> ♪

1962
01:53:02,670 --> 01:53:04,171
♪ <i>This is my heaven, baby</i> ♪

1963
01:53:04,305 --> 01:53:09,443
♪ <i>Day and night in my zone</i> ♪

1964
01:53:09,577 --> 01:53:13,180
♪ <i>We are free of worries</i> ♪

1965
01:53:13,314 --> 01:53:14,849
♪ <i>Stressin' aside</i> ♪

1966
01:53:14,983 --> 01:53:17,217
♪ <i>Take me home</i> ♪

1967
01:53:17,351 --> 01:53:21,722
♪ <i>Free, no worries at all</i> ♪

1968
01:53:24,358 --> 01:53:25,994
Agent, I want an update.

1969
01:53:26,126 --> 01:53:29,196
Still searching, sir.
We haven't found
any sign of Robotnik.

1970
01:53:29,330 --> 01:53:31,565
No one could've
survived that crash.

1971
01:53:31,699 --> 01:53:34,869
He's toast.
Good riddance.

1972
01:53:35,003 --> 01:53:38,138
What a mess
that lunatic made.

1973
01:53:38,272 --> 01:53:40,909
Sir, there's something else.

1974
01:53:41,042 --> 01:53:44,946
When we were wiping Robotnik
off our database,
we found something.

1975
01:53:45,080 --> 01:53:49,017
A file buried deep
in our system
and dating back over 50 years.

1976
01:53:49,149 --> 01:53:50,684
